<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I read somewhere (Old EQ Enchanter I think) that the time in which you turn in the completed RedV quest directly correlates to the reward of the bull smasher.  Any who, try going to the popular sites and doing a search for RedV and Bullsmasher.  As a Gnome Enchanter I did the quest like 5-6 times and recived the Bullsmasher, I've done the quest 10-15 times after that and have gotten nothing or Absorbers. When I got the Bullsmasher it was early evening (8ish EST)  Good luck.  Oh and I'm on the Veeshan Server, but before you assult me with requests for the Bullsmasher I gave yes gave it to a newbie cleric a long time ago and have since forgotten his name.  Good Luck and Good Fortune</font></td></tr></table>
