<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: DeYoung</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-09 09:47:22</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The GemChoppers love my woodelf ranger.  I've collected Red V's box and filled it and returned it to Manik about 12 times with no Bullsmasher yet.  The box you create from Red V is a LORE NO DROP item.  The rusted blackboxes from rogue clockworks near the mino caves are just NO DROP.  They will not work I'm sure.  He gives me exp and faction and some item (usually a shield or some patchwork or Iony's Absorber) when I give him Red V's box but nothing if I give him a rogue clockworks box.  If you give him two of the rogue clockworks boxes at a time this satisifies his other quest and he gives exp, faction, and minor cash loot.  I will continue to try Red V for the Bullsmasher, a cleric friend of mine could use it and I like to give presents!</font></td></tr></table>
